Summer’s heating up, and your punch game should too! 🍹☀️ Ready to make this deliciousness yourself? Here’s what you’ll need ↓

🍓 1 cup firm strawberries, hulled
🍊 1 orange
🍋 1 lime
🍋 1 lemon
🍍 4 cups fruit juice (orange, pineapple, or a mix)
🍒 1 cup cranberry or pomegranate juice
✨ 2 cups ginger ale, lemon-lime soda, or sparkling water

How to make it:

1️⃣ Slice all fruit using the Mando Junior.

2️⃣ Combine all juices and fruit in a pitcher or punch bowl and stir.

3️⃣ Right before serving, pour in the bubbles and gently mix.

4️⃣ Serve over ice and enjoy your new go-to summer sip.

Tag a friend you’d share this with and save this post to make it later. 😋 #TupperwareBrand
